\text{span}(B) = V
V = U_1\oplus\cdots\oplus U_n.
U_1+\cdots+U_n = \{c_1b_1,\ b_1\in B, c_1\in\mathbb{F}\} + \cdots+\{c_nb_n,\ b_n\in B,\ c_n\in\mathbb{F}\}
\sum_{j=1}^n\dim{U_j} = \sum_{j=1}^{n}1 = n = \dim{V}.
